name: The_Mighty_Musstoro
content: The Mighty Musstoro was a hulking Ankura Gungan street wrestler operating in the Center Sphere District of Bartyn's Landing, Lamaredd as of c. 29 BBY. Using a street barker as his representative, the Mighty Musstoro challenged bystanders to a test of strength, with bets. Anyone defeating The Mighty Musstoro was entitled to 100 credits.
